<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <%- include("../../components/head.ejs") %>
  <title>MPC Lab | Tasks</title>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("../../components/main-sidebar.ejs") %>
  <main class="sm:ml-64 p-6">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text">Classroom Tasks</h1>
      <a href="/classrooms/<%= classId %>/tasks/new" class="bg-primary-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-primary-400 transition-colors duration-200">New Task</a>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-background-50 shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-500 mb-2">Task 1: Introduction to AI</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text mb-4 line-clamp-2">
          This task will introduce you to the fundamentals of AI, including machine learning, neural networks, and practical applications...
        </p>
        <a href="/classrooms/<%= classId %>/tasks/1" class="inline-block bg-primary-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-primary-400 transition-colors duration-200">Enter Task</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-background-50 shadow-md rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-500 mb-2">Task 2: Data Structures</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-text mb-4 line-clamp-2">
          In this task, you will learn about the core data structures used in computer science, including arrays, linked lists, stacks...
        </p>
        <a href="/classrooms/<%= classId %>/tasks/2" class="inline-block bg-primary-500 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-primary-400 transition-colors duration-200">Enter Task</a>
      </div>

      <!-- More tasks... -->
    </div>
  </main>
</body>

</html>